Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译 右翼部鸣明 校对 牙牙 Husky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,时间轴 SG 文本处理 谷子 yoyo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,资源搬运 yoyo 特别参考帮助 考生 09
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 我已经快猜到这个惊喜是什么了\NI'm starting to guess the surprise, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了要闭上眼睛噢\NI told you to close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 在这等着\NOkay, wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,萨普莱斯！\NSurprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们买了一艘船！\NWe bought a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 纠正一下 --我们租了一艘船\NUh, correction --We rented a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然现在是暴富了 但是买一艘船\NI may be rich, but buying a boat would be going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,未免也太过了\Na bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一个我从水手们那学的笑话啦\NJust a joke I picked up from some sailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的幽默感总是令人惊讶\NThey have a surprisingly clean sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 这是谁啊\NSteven,who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 葛雷格·宇宙\NUh,Greg Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经弄断我的腿 试着利用海洋\NYou broke my leg trying to use the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,飞回你的母星\Nto fly back to your homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这里青金石壁琉璃 很高兴认识你\NLapis Lazuli. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 那么 我要去启动这艘船了\NGreat! Well,I'll get the boat started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你觉得怎么样\NSo what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这很好了 史蒂文\NIt's nice, Steven...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我不确定自己是怎么考虑的\Nbut I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 我知道你和铁石英\NLook, Lapis, I know you spent a really long time fused
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在海底融合了相当久\Nwith Jasper at the bottom of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你现在已经不再是孔雀石了\Nbut you're not Malachite anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而水是你自身的一部分\NAnd water is a part of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能因为一次糟糕的经历就放弃这部分\NYou can't let one bad experience take that away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一次\NIt was more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就当只是尝试好了\NJust give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓你会感到前所未有的乐趣\NI promise we'll make this the most fun you've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 我…不配拥有这些\NSteven,I...don't deserve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然配了！\NOf course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至给这艘船命名为小琉璃号\NWe even named her Li'l Lappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我会尝试一下的\NOkay. I'll give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 就一下\NBut, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个准备好启程了吗\NYou two ready to set sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 船长！\NAye, aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全速前进--\NFull speed ahe--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你觉得会有人发现吗\NAh, geez, you think anyone will notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喔啊 我想我真的重创了那个码头\NWow, I think I did a number on that dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许其他人应该试试当船长\NMaybe somebody else should take a shot at being captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看 青金石船长？\NWhat do you say, Captain Lazuli?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该当\NI shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上嘛 青金石\NGo for it, Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把控制权给我！\NDon't put me in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 对不起\NOh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我-我不懂驾船的事\NI mean, y-you shouldn't trust me with the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 没关系 不用困扰\NUh, that's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以都当大副 这样就没有竞争压力了\NWe can all be first mates so there's no pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天只能用来嗨！\NOnly fun stuff today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 如果你想的话还是可以戴这顶帽子的\NLapis, you can still wear the hat, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 但是我不想让那东西戴在我身上\NThanks, but I'm not putting that on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们嗨起来 --\NLet's set a course for f-u-u-un!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹 老爹\NDad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你们俩终于玩腻那个喇叭了？\NHey, you two. Finally get enough of that horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啥\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,钓鱼\NCatching fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我来帮忙\NOh, I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼?!!?\NWhat the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这确实是一种 呃 非常拽的钓鱼法\NThat's a pretty uh...fancy way of catching fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为青金石超厉害的！\NThat's 'cause Lapis is supa' strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我 呃 感谢你的好意\NWell, I, uh, appreciate the gesture,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得坚持用\Nbut I-I think it would be safer to stick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,传统的方法比较安全\Nto the old-fashioned way of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 呃…当然\NOh, uh...sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 青金石 那太了不起了\NWow, Lapis!That was ama...zing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你们传统的方法是怎么样的\NSo, how do you fish the old-fashioned way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 非常简单\NOh, it's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你先准备一根钓鱼竿\NYou start with a rod,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在鱼线末端绑上一个钩子\Nand you put a hook on the end of your line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 当你感觉到鱼咬钩了\NAnd then,when you feel a nibble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你就收线把它拉上来\Nyou reel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\NAnd there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你给自己钓了一条鱼来吃！\NYou've caught yourself a fish to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是鱼为什么要咬钩\NBut why would a fish ever bite a hook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你要放上鱼饵\NYou got to bait it --put something on it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道鱼喜欢什么 像虫子或者20刀的纸币之类的\Nyou know it wants,like a worm or a $20 bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我示范给你看\NHere, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,钓鱼\NFishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上钩的那一部分要什么时候开始\NWhen does the fish part happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有些时候 钓鱼的意义不在于渔获多少\NWell, sometimes it isn't about the fish you keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而在于你与身边的人共度的好时光\Nbut the company you catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 鱼咬钩了!\NWhoa!I got a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 来试试\NLapis, here!Give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那样拿着竿然后收线\NHold it just like that and reel it in slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样？\NLike this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没错 看起来是条大鱼！\NYou got it. It looks like a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石\NLapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的 青金石\NYou got it, Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,把它钓上来\NReel it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它…拽的…力气好大！\NIt's...pulling...so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看来租鱼竿\NLooks likethis pole rental turned
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,得变成买鱼竿了\Ninto a pole purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你在与那野兽的斗争中非常给力\NBut you did a great job tangling with that beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是-是啊\NY-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不用为没钓上的那条鱼失落\NDon't worry about that one getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 谢谢你\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 今天我的冒险任务也到上限了\NWelp, that's my adventure quota for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我去驾驶室 有什么事找我就吆喝一声\NI'll be at the controls. Holler if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官 青金石 你…\NYes, sir!Lapis, what do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石？\NLapis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你在干什么呢\NHey. Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得我需要坐一会儿\NI just thought I'd sit for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在鱼竿折断之前 你看起来\NYou looked like a real pro fisher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是个钓鱼行家\Nbefore the pole snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,钓鱼确实扫兴了点\NSo, fishing was a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们还有其他的项目可以嗨\NBut I-I got something that'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沙壶球\NShuffleboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才怎么了\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 怎么了\NYeah. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 你可以过来一下吗\NSteven!You got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都没事吧 大副老爹\NIs everything okay,First Mate Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 你听到了吗\NShh!You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 没有\NUhhh...no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,船好像停下了\NI guess it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想船应该是哪里坏了\NI think something's wrong with the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊天哪 舵叶被卡住了\NAw, geez, something's throwing off the rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道现在是什么情况\NI don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,使用指南也没有用\Nand this owner's manual is no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那上面基本上是关于日光浴\NIt's mostly advice on sun tanning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有鱼子酱要配什么饼干的建议\Nand what crackers go with caviar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那鱼子酱要配什么饼干？\NWell, what crackers go with caviar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,水饼干\NWater crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个声音\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,诶玛 我的引擎啊\NOh, crud!The engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不懂怎么修引擎\NI don't know how to fix an engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这次旅程可能要多耽误一会儿了\NThis trip might be a Little longer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小伙计\Nthan we thought,little buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石\NLapis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我有些不那么好的消息\NUm...I have some not-so-good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎出了问题\NThere's trouble with the engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能要在海上困一阵子了\Nand we might be stuck out here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NI'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我的错\NThis whole thing is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让你开心 但是现在一切都搞砸了\NI just wanted you to have fun. but e-everything's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,早知道我不应该拉你来的\NI shouldn't have made you come on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的错 我才应该被怪罪\NIt's my fault. I'm the one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的努力试着享受这次旅行\NI'm really trying to enjoy it out here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我无法停止回忆融合成孔雀石的时候\NI can't stop thinking about being fused as Malachite,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是如何把她困在海底\Nhow I used all my strength to hold her down in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,又是如何努力对抗铁石英\Nand how I was always battling against Jasper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让她不能与我分开\Nto keep her bound to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在不再是这样了\NBut it's not like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用和铁石英在一起了\NYou don't have to be with Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是重点 我 --\NThat's not it. I --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她了\NI miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？！\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们融合太久了\NWe were fused for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…她很坏\NBut...she's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是更坏的那个 我已经做了很多坏事\NI'm terrible! I did horrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我-我弄断了你爸爸的腿 我盗走了你们地球上的海水\NI-I broke your dad's leg. I stole Earth's ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,继续 继续反驳我啊\NGo on!Tell me I'm wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,终于啊\NFinally!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,铁石英\NJasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为我再也赶不上你了\NI thought I'd never catch up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在跟踪我们？\NYou've been following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在跟踪你\NI've been following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\NStay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你终于打算用盗版玫瑰的技能了？\NThis dulled-down version of Rose Quartz works for you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的盾不应该指向我\NYou're pointing that shield the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她才是你应该害怕的人\NShe's the one you should be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的不对\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你可骗不了我\NYou can't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经见识过你的力量了\NI've seen what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我已经很残暴了 但是你 --\NI thought I was a brute, but you --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你简直是怪物\Nyou're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石不想再与你有任何瓜葛了\NLapis doesn't want anything to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们…\NThis is between...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人之间的事！\Nus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文！\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请再次与我融合吧\NLet's be Malachite again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…你要这么做\NWhy...would you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前对融合的观念完全是错的 但是你让我理解了\NI was wrong about fusion. You made me understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,孔雀石比我们两个都更强 更大\NMalachite was bigger and stronger than both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能上天！\NWe could fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 别听她的\NLapis, don't listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,少管闲事！\NStay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前对你很坏\NI was terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢夺取你的一切\NI liked taking everything out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我必须这么做 我- 我讨厌你\NI needed to. I-I hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的融合太糟糕了\NIt was bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不会再是那样了 我已经改变了\NIt'll be better this time. I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经改变了我\NYou've changed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我才可以驾驭你这样的力量\NI'm the only one who can handle your kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一起将无人能挡\NTogether,we'll be unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样的关系是不健康的\NWhat we had wasn't healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没喜欢过跟你在一起的感觉 我跟你再也不可能了\NI never want to feel like I felt with you -- never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧\NSo just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-青金石 -她已经说拒绝了\N-Lapis! -She said, "No"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要纠缠她了\NLeave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这全是你的错\NThis is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要灭了你\NI'll shatter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 你做到了\NLapis, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩没事吧\NAre you two okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啥\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才发生了啥\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 说来话长\NUh, it's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想最后我还是得买那船\NI guess I bought a boat after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 对不起 老爹\NEhh, sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 嘿 从这上面看海倒是挺美的\NBut, hey, the ocean's really beautiful from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\NIt is.
